sourcesContent: import React, { useState } from "react"; import axios from "axios"; export const Donate = () => { const [donor, setDonor] = useState({ name: "", gender:"", birthyear:"", mobile:"", email: "", address: "", }); const handleInput = (e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; setDonor({...donor,[name]:value}); }; const handleSign = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); setDonor({ name: "", gender:"", birthyear:"", mobile:"", email: "", address: "", }) } let year =[] for(let i=1990;i<=2023;i++){ year.push(i) } console.log(year) return( <>
